commentPostTextItems.html: That's it Pakistan win by 150 runs and wins the series 5-0. The players shake hands as they head off to the pavilion. Pakistan's 11th consecutive ODI win. Asif and Afridi picking up three wickets each. Bangladesh were never in the chase after they lost early wickets. Mohammad Asif picks up the Man-of-the-Match award and Salman Butt picks up the Man-of-the-Series award.

Thanks for being with us and it has been a pleasure bringing you the live ball-by-ball commentary. It is bye from all of us here at Cricinfo. Please do join us again for next match, which is a Twenty20 match tomorrow, April 20. Until then, I am Binoy George and along with Raymond signing off.
